{"tid":390151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔想殘廢」　前利物浦左閘31歲退休","createTime":"2017-09-07T00:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T12:38:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2634fccc09aaf7d10d82a108c43f5b6f7ca5d2","tid":390151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www1.pictures.zimbio.com/gi/Newcastle+United+v+Liverpool+Premier+League+btoqDct63JCl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.pictures.zimbio.com%2Fgi%2FNewcastle%2BUnited%2Bv%2BLiverpool%2BPremier%2BLeague%2BbtoqDct63JCl.jpg&h=42b6406a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得荷西安歷基？呢位效力過利物浦、紐卡素嘅西班牙左後衞，自2016年回流西班牙效力薩拉戈薩，表現已不大如前；周三佢更加宣佈，因為長期傷患，決定退休，31歲就結束球員生涯。<br />\n<br />\n荷西安歷基雖然未為利物浦、紐卡素等球隊贏過主要錦標，亦都未嘗大國腳滋味，不過左路側擊力強，一度是紅軍主力。佢接受西班牙《馬卡報》訪問時，傷感咁講：「當2013年我接受完手術，以為3個月就可以復出，但最終休息2年，我搵過5個醫生幫助，都冇辦法徹底解決我嘅問題。我上季為薩拉戈薩上陣30場，每一次比賽完，膝蓋舊患部位，就腫到一個波咁大，而且三日時間都冇辦法落床。我已經唔可以不依靠藥物繼續練習或者比賽，我好擔心自己40、50歲無法再行路，為咗未來人生，只可以放棄足球事業。」"},{"pid":"88309c720fbedd5e9163b4a16cf65411afad69ed","tid":390151,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97513f4478a935896ebba232c38be497f8cc618","tid":390151,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"每一次比賽完，膝蓋舊患部位，就腫到一個波咁大，<br />\n咩傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e694d1d268a5d5ee5d4cbde5bd92970fa15c9e","tid":390151,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:06:33.000Z","msg":"其實佢打閘真係唔錯<br />\n點解連入選國家隊打下友誼賽後備都冇機會"},{"pid":"46fb46b6a69ba6178d30df8f507bd8a5e2563aeb","tid":390151,"uid":50882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:09:04.000Z","msg":"有速度有身位 1對1 真係未見過人過到佢"},{"pid":"3b1462fcc06a76b2765587326e85cd2122838e10","tid":390151,"uid":40938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"終於都肯正式退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都準退休左幾年 日日都係帶住個老婆遊山玩水"},{"pid":"647c11d57ec299fddd66f96c5433f7d9314d484a","tid":390151,"uid":59903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一次比賽完，膝蓋舊患部位，就腫到一個波咁大，<br />\n咩傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n京治都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212c39a06c8b1298fa035300f448b405ec7c63c3","tid":390151,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢打閘真係唔錯<br />\n點解連入選國家隊打下友誼賽後備都冇機會</blockquote><br />\n因為迪保on9"},{"pid":"c8669ab9ec21cdc98b389b9f6d839ca363d11379","tid":390151,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一次比賽完，膝蓋舊患部位，就腫到一個波咁大，<br />\n咩傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大傷完就咁<br />\n原本係穩居正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2faf44a7092c7e52949b42bb0c82e375b2f3ab1","tid":390151,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實佢打閘真係唔錯<br />\n點解連入選國家隊打下友誼賽後備都冇機會</blockquote><br />\n因為迪保on9</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母用埋d咩卡迪維拿<br />\n下下比人爆"},{"pid":"4540fe0a2a3